{
  "stem": "25639.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I have pictures of-- a picture of her [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But to get back to Auschwitz, then we-- we travelled, I think, two or three days, and we landed in-- in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was my second camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was really glad to be alive, but I-- I missed my mother and my sister sorely after Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In fact, through research, I found that I must have been on the-- on the last transport to-- from Auschwitz to Bergen-Belsen in the year of 1944.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The last transport left Auschwitz on the 30th and arrived in Bergen-Belsen on the 1st.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I guess it was two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because in my research, I found that the-- the train that left there prior to that, to Bergen-Belsen from Auschwitz, was back in previous months, and I knew that that could not have been for me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So through process of elimination, I was able to zero in on that-- on that train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And if that is correct, I arrived in Bergen-Belsen on January 1st, 1945.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there in Bergen-Belsen, we were placed in huge canvas barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were not wooden barracks like in Auschwitz, but made of canvas-- temporary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because the camp was so full, and so many inmates were transferred there, that they had to build additional shelter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I remember there were no bunk beds there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We arrived in-- in a terrible storm, and we were soaking wet when we arrived in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I mean, we had to walk from the train to our bunk beds, to the camp, and I couldn't believe my eyes when I saw all that mud flowing in under the canvas from the hillside.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
